<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2067] Czech Stemmer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2067</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the CzechAnalyzer is merely stopwords, and there isn&apos;t a czech stemmer in snowball.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch implements the light stemming algorithm described in: &lt;a href=&quot;http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1598600&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot;&gt;http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1598600&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In their measurements, it improves MAP 42%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The analyzer does not use this stemmer if LUCENE_VERSION &amp;lt;= 3.0, for back compat.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
